Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This girl is Kouyama Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.59,0:00:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She's twelve and dreams of becoming a singer.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But unfortunately...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:05.78,0:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...she only has one year left to live.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.46,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We, the Shinigami were asked to keep an \Neye on her until the inevitable fate, but...{Completely changed the line, they didn't go to Mitsuki to TELL her, rather they were TOLD to watch over her until she meets her fate in a year time.}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:11.69,0:00:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Today, she's become an adult...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...and she performed incredibly in the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Aren't we...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...changing her destiny?!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well then...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.17,0:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.64,0:00:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,460)\be1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.10,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,460)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.00,0:00:35.01,Episode Title,,0,0,0,Sign,{\pos(330,340)\bord2.5}The Promise With Eichi-kun
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This is all your fault, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Didn't that girl pass the audition?!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Man.. I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I didn't think she would actually be chosen.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.98,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't talk like that about other people's lives!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.11,0:00:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're shouting, Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:50.17,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It couldn't be that you've forgotten\Nwhat our job here is?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}To make sure that when her one year is up...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.10,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...she won't refuse to come with us, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.09,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Exactly!
Dialogue: 2,0:00:59.09,0:01:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So then, it doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.74,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...whether or not she passed the audition.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:05.79,0:01:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...not!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.92,0:01:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She was willing to return to the house with us...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Now that she's become a singer... it'll be \N troublesome to have to follow her around.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You let a human like her know the truth...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...and even turned her into a sixteen-year old!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I won't forgive you for a stunt like this!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:22.65,0:01:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You two seem to be so close.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.31,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.81,0:01:30.40,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}I-Is that how it looks?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:31.61,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, after all...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We are...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...the ones who silence the tears of children.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:35.53,0:01:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The Shinigami Duo...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...Spring Onion Ramen!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm really grateful for everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:44.29,0:01:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh? Oh... It was nothing.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.04,0:01:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...that song you sang at the audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.50,0:01:46.33,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}What is this?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.88,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}Why am I the only one being left out?!
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what song was that?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That was...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...the song my father, a musician, wrote.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Really...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:01.73,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}For some reason, I can't seem to remember \Nwhether or not I've heard it before...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hold it!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.89,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't think that just because you passed \Nthe audition, you've become an adult!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-When I'm in this body, I'm all grown up!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hmm... so then...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.94,0:02:15.65,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,410)\be1}Meroko!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Stop harassing her!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Oh... but...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.66,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I can't go home like this, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh? Oh. Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Amazing...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I turned back to normal.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yep. Your chest returned to normal, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.68,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}P-Please don't stare at me like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Geez... you're so stingy.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.75,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...really plan on becoming a singer?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I promised, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Promised?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}My promise... with Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wait, who is that?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Your sweetheart?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}H-He's not my sweetheart...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...yet.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So that means...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...he's the one you're longing for?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...two years ago...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...entered a treatment center for the ill.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}While Grandma was traveling abroad...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I stayed there with Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.05,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}He told me his feelings, but before I could answer...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...due to circumstances beyond \Nour control, he left for America.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No, no!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't go, Eichi-kun!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.77,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't cry, Mitsuki.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}America isn't that far away.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.64,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Here... let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Until we meet again...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.16,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...we'll work hard to reach our dreams.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.12,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}For me, it's to be an astronomer.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}And you, a singer.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I love you.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Even though we'll be apart...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I'll look for the moon in the sky.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's why... so I can find you sooner...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.39,0:04:18.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...shine even more brighter.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}More... and more...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}And since then?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Since then?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Haven't you had any contact with him since then?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}For example, mail or an overseas phone call?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well... I have no idea how \Nto get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I accomplish my dream of becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...my name might even reach \Nsomewhere as far as America.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Then surely...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...surely... Eichi-kun will... notice me.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You put your whole heart into this, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Somewhat, I guess.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is it, Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're making such a frightening face.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Scary...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What are you?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:00.05,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I thought you had honest \Nfeelings of becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...but it was all for a guy!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.89,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's just wrong!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If you don't have pure intentions \Nof becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you can't become a good singer!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.37,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...quit singing immediately!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-Why are you saying something like that?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Isn't it great that she's doing it because of a guy?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Not at all!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll... work really hard at singing, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No matter how hard you work, in the back \Nof your mind, you'll always feel like quitting.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That can't be...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I would never want to quit singing.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's right! What part of this is immoral?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What part of doing it for a guy is anyways?!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...such blind faith after being neglected \N for two years is anything but normal!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You've been dumped.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}He's probably already with another girl over there.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}E-Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Why can't you understand that?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's because... it's Eichi-kun, after all!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's foolish.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Cut it out, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Anyways...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...someone as disrespectful of singing as you...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...will never sing again!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:01.52,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hmph!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-Wait... Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Come on, Takuto!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Geez... why is he so mad?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}More importantly...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.22,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what kind of person gets in the way of fate...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Someone who gets in the way of a human's fate...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...may be in love with that human.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}This Eichi...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I'll have to pay special attention to him.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Just what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}When I told you that you shouldn't audition...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I wasn't trying to be mean.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.84,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's impossible because your condition right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Stop it.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...it's over with now, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.04,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You'll be unable to sing for a while...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah... no, I made it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Made it?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.86,0:07:09.11,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I can't tell Sensei what really happened.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.11,0:07:09.91,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.91,0:07:12.58,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I wonder if he would believe that I transformed...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.41,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}and about the Shinigami as well...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What do you mean by "made it"?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It couldn't be that... you passed the audition?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um... well...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.54,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's no use.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.50,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's no way he'd ever believe it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um... I meant modeling.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.68,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Oh... modeling, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, modeling is fine, I suppose.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But from now on, don't do anything rash like this.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}O-Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what'd you do for the application?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,Under {\i1\pos(320,450)\be1}guardian{\i0}...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...did you write your grandmother's name?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um... actually...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Did you put my name down?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}F-Forgive me!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We'll keep it a secret from your grandmother, okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I-Is that okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sure.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I understand your feelings, after all.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's for Eichi-kun, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Y-Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You are not allowed to leave the house.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Leaving the house...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...and having the Doctor take \Nyou to the amusement park...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.57,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Amusement park?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.74,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So that's what we did, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.80,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Next time...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...a simple apology will not suffice.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's enough.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Please excuse yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.88,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hmm...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is that?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}T-This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...from the crane game.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Such an annoying grandmother...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She kept going on and on...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But this means that...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you're one step closer to your dream, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.32,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hey...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What kind of guy is Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}He's a pretty good-looking guy.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.29,0:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How old is he?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We're six years apart, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...right now he's eighteen.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So this is a picture of Eichi-kun when he was sixteen?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sooo cute.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fad(200,0}Such blind faith after being neglected \N for two years is anything but normal!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1\fad(0,300)}You've been dumped.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun couldn't possibly...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}So this is where you've been, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.05,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, that means I have nowhere left to go.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:28.20,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That girl looks like she wants to be alone, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You upset her...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's all you fault, you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.03,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She's upset because you told her she'd been dumped.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Well, that's what I think would have happened by now.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Besides...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.13,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...constantly thinking about a guy who's already\ndumped you is strange in this day and age!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's {\i1\pos(320,450)\be1}strange,{\i0} indeed.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Right?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Always avoiding the truth...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you haven't changed at all, Takuto.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you like her?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}S-Stupid.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I-Isn't this our duty?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Besides, even if I said she was dumped...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.02,0:11:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I was just saying that as a general \Nobservation... I didn't state it very well.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.33,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an8\be1\pos(320,15)}Just as I thought... something is amiss.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Such a matter...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.48,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\an8\be1\pos(320,15)}Takuto is mine!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Here you go!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Fortune telling?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.16,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yep.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll read your fortune for today.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Pick a card.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.12,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Which one is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Today's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's lucky?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Yep. Super Lucky.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The lucky word today is... {\alpha&HFF&}shopping.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}The lucky word today is... shopping!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Something good will definitely happen.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Come on, let's go out.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.27,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Grandma's out today, too.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah, but if I don't ask Tanaka-san...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do you need something, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I want to go out shopping...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But madam said that...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If Grandma learns that you listen to forbidden music...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I wonder what she'll say?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You might get scolded...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Shall we head out?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Where are they going?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.57,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If Meroko's going along, then I'll \Njust leave everything up to her.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.71,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Can you wait here for a little bit, please?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Sure, I understand.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Then... then... just wait a little, please!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Later!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Hmm?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's somewhere I want to go, too...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah... I'm going to use the toilet, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...just wait for me outside.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Shinigami have to use the restroom too, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}She left, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.58,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That girl listened to my suggestion to go out so readily, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mero-Mero Change!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's mine!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's mine, I tell you!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That good thing...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I wonder what it is.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That guy is...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's been a long time, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}E-
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That guy is...?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}T-This can't be real.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's real, all right.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.47,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Although, it's really a lie.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.86,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Once you're with Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.61,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you'll stop wanting to be a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.61,0:14:54.58,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...and Takuto will give up on you too.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.62,Internal Thought,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's for that reason...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm dreaming, aren't I?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.67,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're not dreaming.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Even though I went to America...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I never forgot about you, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...once I heard you'd become a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I hurried back to Japan.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}My becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Who did I hear that from?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}S-Someone I know in the record business.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's how I...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's an amazing coincidence.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It was more than a coincidence...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...it was fate.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Fate...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}By the way, Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...what's with that voice?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}After going to America...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I suppose that my voice probably changed like so.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}America's so vast... right?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.83,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're so funny.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}R-Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}W-What is it this time?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's something I have to \Napologize to you for, Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I... I sang... for your sake...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I thought that you might have forgotten about me.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What? It's for that?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.89,0:15:59.89,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Will you still... like me?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}O-Of course.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Back then... I...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.35,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I couldn't properly answer, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.16,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Now... I also... about you...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.38,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}L-
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm... I'm... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.84,Overlap,,0,0,0,Dialogue (Overlap),{\pos(320,410)\be1}Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.79,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Shinigami-san.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That isn't Eichi.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.01,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's Meroko.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}We Shinigami are capable of transformation.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Is... that so..?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.73,0:16:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Eichi-kun... has no reason to be here, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I've made you wait!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Is something wrong, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Your face looks pale.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Come, let's go home.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That was low!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You've really done it now!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I thought it was a good idea...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}How was that a good idea?!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Someone's serious matter...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...a person's pure feelings...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...you were just toying with them!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You think that apologizing will solve this?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.46,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Wait.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.27,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Pure... didn't you just say that they were immoral?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.08,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I said that?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You sure did!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}"What part of doing it for a guy\Nis moral?", something like that.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.71,0:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.16,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That was about becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That and this are two totally unrelated matters!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I guess that I was pretty cruel...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But all that stuff about Eichi...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...being dumped and all...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What are you going to do about it, Takuto?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Don't you think that your words hurt her?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:12.23,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}What I said about you being dumped \Njust me being a devil's advocate...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I didn't mean it.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}It's just a possibility.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No... that's...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.32,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.24,0:18:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}No.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I was also at fault.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I really believed in Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...no matter what was said... I wouldn't be worried.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}That's why I won't be confused anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:33.71,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I... I love Eichi-kun!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}But, just as much as that...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I love singing!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I love him...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...then I have to believe in him!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I have to do my best to believe in him!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}If I don't, then my dream will never come true!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.14,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}These feelings...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...will never be impure!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}Do whatever you want to do.
