Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}You will?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}My blood will...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...always be inside you, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...I'll always be able to transform you.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}When I'm not with you...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}...use this whistle to call me.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(320,450)\be1}I'll fly to you.
